4 Best Thai food that I have found in Phoenix.  The service is great and I always have a good meal here.  They are very accommodating to alterations to the menu and specific requests.  My favorites are the Pad See Ew, Pad Thai, Veggie Lover, and the Tom Ka Soup.  One of my staples for lunch every week.
