5 This restaurant is located inside the Mekong Plaza - my GPS kept circling - so beware. The ambiance is open and asian. The server was gracious and attentive. The food was light, fresh and flavorful. A ton of Vegetarian options! We had the veggie rolls and a pot of soup; the pot of soup had a flame coming out of the middle of the bowl. It was groovy! My date had red curry and I had pork noodles - excellent portion size!  I would recommend this restaurant and will be back. 5 stars! Solid!
